query: SELECT 101010 AS CODLOCAL, P.CODPROD, LTRIM(RTRIM(P.DESCRPROD)) AS DESCRPROD, SUM(ISNULL(E.ESTOQUE,0)) AS TOTAL_ESTOQUE FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFEST] E JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFPRO] P ON P.CODPROD = E.CODPROD WHERE E.CODLOCAL = 101010 GROUP BY P.CODPROD, P.DESCRPROD ORDER BY P.DESCRPROD;
originalQuery: SELECT 101010 AS CODLOCAL, P.CODPROD, LTRIM(RTRIM(P.DESCRPROD)) AS DESCRPROD, SUM(ISNULL(E.ESTOQUE,0)) AS TOTAL_ESTOQUE FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFEST] E JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFPRO] P ON P.CODPROD = E.CODPROD WHERE E.CODLOCAL = 101010 GROUP BY P.CODPROD, P.DESCRPROD ORDER BY P.DESCRPROD;
